RNAseq LMB2

Thoenen et al.AMPO formation

Lisa Thoenen & Christine Pestalozzi

2024-05-13

Set settings

set working directory to source file location

Packages

Library loading, setting up misc functions

read in data

Read in RNAseq output from DESeq2 and list of bxd cluster genes.

Filter significantly regulated genes (based on BH-corrected P value < 0.05)

  • 108 genes are significantly differentially expressed
  • 101 of them are upregulated.

Read in the kmer data from comparative genomics done on selected Microbacterium genomes.

group genes into RNAseq significant and kmer signal significant

Plot

Fig S9c and S9d S9c) adjusted p-value vs log2FC: only genes who could be assessed (i.e.padj not NA) are shown. S9d) mean gene expression vs log2FC: genes with mean expression above 25000are removed for better visibility (rRNAs, tRNA)
